[[Image:NGC_4414_(NASA-med).jpg|thumb]]
'''絮結螺旋星系'''是[[螺旋星系|螺旋星系]]的一種，是相對於[[宏觀螺旋星系|宏觀螺旋星系]]的一種機能<ref>COSMOS - SAO Encyclopedia of Astronomy, [http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cms/astro/cosmos/G/Grand+Design+Spiral "Grand Design Spiral"] {{Wayback|url=http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cms/astro/cosmos/G/Grand+Design+Spiral |date=20190415195432 }} (accessed 23 April 2010)</ref>。不同於''宏觀''螺旋星系顯而易見的旋臂結構，''[[wikt:絮結|絮結]]''星系的[[螺旋星系#結構|旋臂]]是零散、不連續的<ref>COSMOS - SAO Encyclopedia of Astronomy, [http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cms/astro/cosmos/F/Flocculent+Spiral "Flocculent Spiral"] {{Wayback|url=http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cms/astro/cosmos/F/Flocculent+Spiral |date=20110413012455 }} (accessed 23 April 2010)</ref>。大約30%的螺旋星系的旋臂是絮結的，10%是宏觀的，而其餘的是"多臂"的<ref>Case Western Reserve University, '''Chris Mihos''', ''ASTR222 - Spring 2008'', [http://burro.cwru.edu/Academics/Astr222/Galaxies/Spiral/spiral.html "Spiral Structure"] {{Wayback|url=http://burro.cwru.edu/Academics/Astr222/Galaxies/Spiral/spiral.html |date=20190608213202 }} (accessed 23 April 2010)</ref>，而"多臂"的類型經常會參雜入絮結的結構 <ref>University of Virginia, '''Mark Whittle''', ''ASTR 553/554 : Extragalactic Astronomy (2007)'',  [http://www.astro.virginia.edu/class/whittle/astr553/Topic05/Lecture_5.html "Lecture 5: Spiral Galaxies"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.astro.virginia.edu/class/whittle/astr553/Topic05/Lecture_5.html |date=20100707135532 }} (accessed 23 April 2010)</ref>。

絮結螺旋星系的原型是[[NGC_2841|NGC 2841]]<ref name="Elmegreen-1981-CH3">"A Near-Infrared Atlas of Spiral Galaxies", '''Debra Meloy Elmegreen''', [http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/level5/Elmegreen/Elm3.html "CH3. Discussion"] {{Wayback|url=http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/level5/Elmegreen/Elm3.html |date=20110126202152 }} (accessed 23 April 2010)</ref>。

